- **Node-20 CI deprecation** — bump pinned action SHAs to Node-24-compatible before 2026-06-16.
- **settings.json bun permission** — decide commit-to-team vs leave-local (see Section 4).
- **patterns.ts header** — was fixed for M2; verify still accurate after FU-6 (cosmetic).

